Demo observed values for gis model

Source: R/demo_gis_values_log.R
demo_gis_values_log.Rd

A dataset containing demo observed log transformed gis values for model 44. Stored as .csv: demo_gis_values_log <- utils::read.csv( system.file("extdat", "environmental-test-data-model-44-log.csv", package = "rict"), check.names = F )

demo_gis_values_log
